text: Cloacina elegans is a species of parasitic nematodes in the family Chabertiidae. Members of the species are parasites of marsupials in Australia. == References == == External links == * Cloacina elegans at gbif.org Category:Strongylida Category:Nematodes described in 1938 Category:Fauna of Australia Category:Parasitic nematodes of mammals Category:Parasites of marsupials Category:Marsupials of Australia
